title: Getting Out of a Rut!
itunes:title: Getting Out of a Rut!
description:
Episode 163 - As humans, we all get in ruts. We all have days where we are completely unmotivated and don't want to put in any work. In this episode I give my top 3 tips to getting yourself out of a rut.
